<div class="container text-center">
  <p>Hi there <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

  <p>Sadly, your account has been locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign in attempts. Maybe you don't remember it due to the amount of passwords you have accumulated over the years or maybe you haven't had enough coffee yet. We don't judge.</p>

  <p>Whatever the reason,we'll need you to just click the link below to unlock your account:</p>

  <p><%= link_to 'Unlock my account', unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token) %></p>

  <p>Easy enough right?!</p>
</div>
